<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="policy-header">
    <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-body">

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>BY RITUEL is operated by Doriano Van de Weyer, based in Belgium. We are the data controller for the personal data collected through byrituel.com.</p>
      <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@byrituel.com">hello@byrituel.com</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you place an order or create an account, we collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name and email address</li>
        <li>Billing and shipping address</li>
        <li>Payment information (processed securely by Shopify Payments — we never store card details)</li>
        <li>Order history and preferences</li>
        <li>IP address and browsing behaviour on our site (via cookies)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Why We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>We process your data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Process and fulfil your orders</li>
        <li>Send order confirmations and shipping updates</li>
        <li>Respond to your customer service requests</li>
        <li>Send marketing emails (only with your consent)</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Our legal basis for processing is: contract performance (orders), legitimate interest (site improvement), and consent (marketing emails).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to make our website work, analyse traffic, and show you relevant ads. You can manage your cookie preferences using the banner shown on your first visit. For full details, see our Cookie Policy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Who We Share Data With</h2>
      <p>We only share your data with trusted third parties necessary to operate the store:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Shopify</strong> — our e-commerce platform (stores your order and account data)</li>
        <li><strong>Shipping partners</strong> — to deliver your order</li>
        <li><strong>Payment processors</strong> — Shopify Payments / PayPal</li>
        <li><strong>Email marketing tools</strong> — only if you have opted in</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We never sell your data to third parties.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>As a resident of Belgium and the EU, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
        <li>Object to or restrict processing</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time (for marketing emails, unsubscribe at the bottom of any email)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@byrituel.com">hello@byrituel.com</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
      <p>If you are unsatisfied with our response, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Belgian Data Protection Authority (APD/GBA): <a href="https://www.dataprotectionauthority.be" target="_blank">www.dataprotectionauthority.be</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain order and customer data for 7 years as required by Belgian tax law. Marketing data is retained until you unsubscribe or request deletion.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The most current version will always be available at byrituel.com/pages/privacy-policy.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

